    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>用base64对关键词进行两次编码，浏览器客户端用javascript进行两次解码。对于支持javascript的浏览器来说透明，目的是防止关键词过滤。</p>

<!--more-->

<p>如
<script src='/javascripts/base64.js' type='text/javascript'> </script> <span id='base64_block'>Q2lEcG1MTG5nYXZsb3BrZzVyQ1I1TGk3SU9pSHF1ZVVzU0RwZ3BQbHNJL2x1Yk1nNklPaDZaU201cmFiSU9heG4rYXp2ZWF3a1NEa3VhRG92NUhsdWJNZzVyT1Y2TDJ1NVlxZklPaWx2K2lYanlEbWxyRG5sb1lnQ2c9PQ==</span> <script type='text/javascript'> var line_name = 'base64_block';var content = document.getElementById(line_name).innerHTML;document.getElementById(line_name).innerHTML=Base64.decode(Base64.decode(content));</script></p>

]]></content>
